The Thriller Bark arc is about to turn terrifying! Luffy attempts to track down Moria and take back what he has lost.  Usopp tries to overcome his cowardliness and use bag of tricks to take down Perona.  Nami is on her way down the aisle at an undead wedding and Zoro clashes with a zombie samurai in order to collect a new blade.  Things are starting to look up when the Straw Hats are faced with an imposing menace the likes of which they have never seen.  They must withstand Oars, powered by Luffy's shadow, and find a way to overcome this insurmountable evil.  Will the Straw Hats make it to dawn alive?  How will they defeat the powerful enemies they are each facing?  Find out the answers by watching the next exciting episode...or this collection!
Thriller Bark is such an epic ark
I received it right away. Love one piece :)

I love One Piece! It's so great that they actually try. The English voices are great and the transition from japanese to dub is pretty good. Funimation nailed it in my opinion and they are going at a pretty good pace. Keep up the great work. I'm an avid supporter and I own all the voyages. I don't wait for the season collections.
If you love the dub you'll love this.
Funny and silly but fun to watch even as a teenager.
Awesome stuff great anime and manga!
This is a fantastic show. If you are new to anime this is a great gateway.
The only issue i had is that disc one came in disc two's packaging and vice versa..........Other than that always a solid show
